question: Based on the following hair salon review, what are the atypical aspects for a hair salon? context: Mary gives fabulous cuts -- I'd been going to her at the Saturn Club for years, so didn't hesitate about following her to Deluxe. This newly renovated space is nice and modern and in a convenient location (next to bicycle therapy). Mary also tries hard to accommodate your schedule.
Haven't tried any of the other stylists yet, but Mary's great! 
Haircuts are about $45.

labels: [['The salon is a community art space. There is always great local art for sale on the walls, the occasional yoga class where proceeds go to local community organizations, and beauty nights where you get to learn about and test products for free. preds: ['The salon doubles as a community art space. There is always great local art for sale on the walls, the occasional yoga class where proceeds go to local community organizations, and beauty nights where you get to learn about and test products for free.', 'The salon offers waxing, spray tanning, makeup, and bridal services.', '', 'The salon provides drinks, snacks, free wifi, coloring books (for adults), beauty bar and much more.', '', 'The salon has an art gallery and a fashion store.', 'The salon uses their anniversary party every year as a fundraiser for local causes.', 'The salon owner draws anthropomorphic coyotes in their ads and the owner also helps a dog saving organization.', '']
labels: [['The salon is a community art space. There is always great local art for sale on the walls, the occasional yoga class where proceeds go to local community organizations, and beauty nights where you get to learn about and test products for free. A customer won a jar of organic, vegan body scrub at a beauty night.'], ['The staff also holds tutorials on hair as well as makeup. The salon offers waxing, spray tanning, makeup, and bridal services.'], ['There is an ATM in the salon.'], ['The salon has free wifi. They have coloring books for adults.'], [''], ['The salon is a shop as well as a studio. They have a little art gallery with art on the walls done by local artists. The designer of the fashion part of the store has dresses with sleek lines.'], ['The salon uses its anniversary party every year as a fundraiser for local causes in addition to all the other fundraising they do throughout the year to help various local organizations and individuals in need.'], [''], ['']]

preds: ['The salon doubles as a community art space. There is always great local art for sale on the walls, the occasional yoga class where proceeds go to local community organizations, and beauty nights where you get to learn about and test products for free.', 'The salon offers waxing, spray tanning, makeup, and bridal services.', '', 'The salon has drinks, snacks, free wifi, coloring books (for adults), beauty bar and much more.', '', 'The salon has a fashion part of the store.', 'The salon uses their anniversary party every year as a fundraiser for local causes.', "The salon' owner draws anthropomorphic coyotes in their ads. The owner also helps a dog saving organization.", '']
labels: [['The salon is a community art space. There is always great local art for sale on the walls, the occasional yoga class where proceeds go to local community organizations, and beauty nights where you get to learn about and test products for free. A customer won a jar of organic, vegan body scrub at a beauty night.'], ['The staff also holds tutorials on hair as well as makeup. The salon offers waxing, spray tanning, makeup, and bridal services.'], ['There is an ATM in the salon.'], ['The salon has free wifi. They have coloring books for adults.'], [''], ['The salon is a shop as well as a studio. They have a little art gallery with art on the walls done by local artists. The designer of the fashion part of the store has dresses with sleek lines.'], ['The salon uses its anniversary party every year as a fundraiser for local causes in addition to all the other fundraising they do throughout the year to help various local organizations and individuals in need.'], [''], ['']]

Walk ins are welcome, but I'd recommend making an appointment.", 'The salon offers exercise classes.', 'The salon has a playful spirit and listens to her needs.', 'The salon offers a certified massage therapist (that is also certified in prenatal massage), yoga on Monday nights, and photography services by the talented Jammy Straub.', "The salon actively and passionately cares about our environment. Sylvia's product line, Aveda, is derived from 100% natural ingredients.", 'The salon is bilingual as their team speaks English and Spanish.', 'The salon allows you to donate a buck or two to charity which I appreciated.', 'The salon has a steam room.', 'The salon has adopted a more boutique-style environment, with artwork on the walls and they even have a tattoo studio attached.']
